column2: SELECT g.ra, g.dec, s.z, s.zerr, g.cModelMag_u - g.extinction_u as cmu, g.cModelMag_g-g.extinction_g as cmg, g.cModelMag_r-g.extinction_r as cmr, g.cModelMag_i-g.extinction_i as cmi, g.cModelMag_z-g.extinction_z as cmz, g.cModelMagErr_u, g.cModelMagErr_g, g.cModelMagErr_r, g.cModelMagErr_i, g.cModelMagErr_z, n.distance, pz.z as photoz, pz.zerr as photoz_err into mydb.mmt2 from galaxytag g CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (#, #, #) AS n left outer join specphoto s on s.objid = n.objid left outer join photoz pz on pz.objid = n.objid WHERE N.objID = g.ObjID and g.modelMag_r< #
